data.description: Spacious home with split floor plan on oversized lot in Gravette in Patriot Park Subdivision. This home features brand new water proof pergo flooring, new roof, new hot water heater and new wood privacy fence.  6x4 Metal shed to convey. Just a couple of minutes from all of the conveniences of Gravette... it's walking distance to the ball park, less than 2 minutes from the grocery store and about 10 minutes to I49 in Centerton. This property would make a great starter home and it has the perfect backyard for kids!  It also qualifies for a rural development loan! Make an offer today!
